Package vpm.gui_prototype.models.PetStuff

Class Cat

java.lang.Object
vpm.gui_prototype.models.PetStuff.Pet
vpm.gui_prototype.models.PetStuff.Cat
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPet
public class Cat extends Pet
Represents a Cat, extending the abstract Pet class. This class includes constructors for creating a new cat or fetching one from the database, as well as methods to determine happiness and hunger decrement intervals.
